Triggers
  DistrRequestUpdate 
-- =============================================
-- Author:		<Author,,Name>
-- Create date: <Create Date,,>
-- Description:	<Description,,>
-- =============================================
CREATE TRIGGER DistrRequestUpdate
   ON  dbo.DistrRequest
   AFTER  INSERT,UPDATE
AS 
BEGIN
declare @CityId uniqueidentifier,
@DistributerId uniqueidentifier ,
@DocId uniqueidentifier ,
@Address nvarchar(500)
select @CityId = i.ToCityId,
@DistributerId = i.DistrId,
@DocId = i.Id
from inserted as i
select @Address = Address from DistrCity where DistributorId = @DistributerId and CityId = @CityId
update DistrRequest set Address = @Address where Id = @DocId
END

View MovementView
Query
 
CREATE VIEW ${schemaName}.${viewName}
AS
SELECT        dbo.Movement.ID, dbo.Movement.MovementName, dbo.WarehouseName.WHName AS SourceWH, dbo.WarehouseName.WHIndex AS SourceIndex, dbo.Movement.SourceWHID, dbo.Movement.SourceStateID, 
                         dbo.Movement.DestWHID, dbo.Movement.DestStateID, dbo.Movement.EDIEnabled, WarehouseName_1.WHName AS DestWH, WarehouseName_1.WHIndex AS DestIndex, dbo.ProductState.State AS SourceState, 
                         ProductState_1.State AS DestState, dbo.Movement.Description, dbo.Movement.Active
FROM            dbo.WarehouseName AS WarehouseName_1 RIGHT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.Movement ON WarehouseName_1.ID = dbo.Movement.DestWHID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.ProductState AS ProductState_1 ON dbo.Movement.DestStateID = ProductState_1.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.ProductState ON dbo.Movement.SourceStateID = dbo.ProductState.ID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.WarehouseName ON dbo.Movement.SourceWHID = dbo.WarehouseName.ID

mdlz.dbo.FindProductBruttoBySapCode 
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[FindProductBruttoBySapCode](@sapCode nvarchar(512))
RETURNS decimal(18,2)
AS
BEGIN
	declare @vol decimal(18,2)
	set @sapCode = substring(@sapCode, patindex('%[^0]%', @sapCode), 10)
	
	set @vol=(select top 1 Product.UnitWeight from Product where 
		substring(SapCode, patindex('%[^0]%', SapCode), 10)=@sapCode)
	
	return isnull(@vol,0)
END

mdlz.dbo.fn_diagramobjects 
	CREATE FUNCTION dbo.fn_diagramobjects() 
	RETURNS int
	WITH EXECUTE AS N'dbo'
	AS
	BEGIN
		declare @id_upgraddiagrams		int
		declare @id_sysdiagrams			int
		declare @id_helpdiagrams		int
		declare @id_helpdiagramdefinition	int
		declare @id_creatediagram	int
		declare @id_renamediagram	int
		declare @id_alterdiagram 	int 
		declare @id_dropdiagram		int
		declare @InstalledObjects	int
		select @InstalledObjects = 0
		select 	@id_upgraddiagrams = object_id(N'dbo.sp_upgraddiagrams'),
			@id_sysdiagrams = object_id(N'dbo.sysdiagrams'),
			@id_helpdiagrams = object_id(N'dbo.sp_helpdiagrams'),
			@id_helpdiagramdefinition = object_id(N'dbo.sp_helpdiagramdefinition'),
			@id_creatediagram = object_id(N'dbo.sp_creatediagram'),
			@id_renamediagram = object_id(N'dbo.sp_renamediagram'),
			@id_alterdiagram = object_id(N'dbo.sp_alterdiagram'), 
			@id_dropdiagram = object_id(N'dbo.sp_dropdiagram')
		if @id_upgraddiagrams is not null
			select @InstalledObjects = @InstalledObjects + 1
		if @id_sysdiagrams is not null
			select @InstalledObjects = @InstalledObjects + 2
		if @id_helpdiagrams is not null
			select @InstalledObjects = @InstalledObjects + 4
		if @id_helpdiagramdefinition is not null
			select @InstalledObjects = @InstalledObjects + 8
		if @id_creatediagram is not null
			select @InstalledObjects = @InstalledObjects + 16
		if @id_renamediagram is not null
			select @InstalledObjects = @InstalledObjects + 32
		if @id_alterdiagram  is not null
			select @InstalledObjects = @InstalledObjects + 64
		if @id_dropdiagram is not null
			select @InstalledObjects = @InstalledObjects + 128
		
		return @InstalledObjects 
	END
mdlz.dbo.udf_GetNumeric 
CREATE FUNCTION dbo.udf_GetNumeric
(
  @strAlphaNumeric VARCHAR(256)
)
RETURNS VARCHAR(256)
AS
BEGIN
  DECLARE @intAlpha bigINT
  SET @intAlpha = PATINDEX('%[^0-9]%', @strAlphaNumeric)
  BEGIN
    WHILE @intAlpha > 0
    BEGIN
      SET @strAlphaNumeric = STUFF(@strAlphaNumeric, @intAlpha, 1, '' )
      SET @intAlpha = PATINDEX('%[^0-9]%', @strAlphaNumeric )
    END
  END
  declare @res varchar(50)
  set @res = cast(@strAlphaNumeric as varchar(50))
  SET @res=STUFF(@res,1,1,'8')
 
  RETURN @res
END

mdlz.dbo.Calc1 
CREATE procedure [dbo].[Calc1](@ID uniqueidentifier, @Point bit ) as 
--set @ID = 'AC089462-589B-401F-9ADF-0C0E07DBCEC2'
--update Product set Vol =  Width*Height*Length/1000000000
--update Product set Vol = Vol1
--update Product set Vol1 = CEILING( Width*Height*Length/10000000 )/100 where Vol=0
update dbo.OrderAddress set 
TerminalTariff = 0,
MinTerminalTariff=0,
PayWeightSet=0,
TerminalPrice =0,
TransCityPrice=0,
RouteVol=0, 
TransCityTariff =0,
InternalTariff=0,
DatePlan_WOut1=null,
ServiceTiming=null,
PlanService=null,
SendCity = ISNULL(SendCity, 'Домодедово'),
Type = ISNULL([Type], 'LTL')
where OrderId=@ID
SELECT CenterCity, sum(Vol) as Vol, sum(Weight) as Weight, CAST(0 as decimal(18,2)) as PayWeihgt, CAST(0 as decimal(18,2)) as WeightTariff
, CAST(0 as decimal(18,2)) as MinTariff, COUNT(1) as RowQnt,  [Type],  SendCity
into #tmp
  FROM [dbo].[OrderAddressView]
  where OrderId=@ID and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
  group by   CenterCity,  [Type],  SendCity
update #tmp
set PayWeihgt = case when Vol*250>Weight then Vol*250 else Weight end

update #tmp set WeightTariff = t.Tariff, MinTariff=t.MinPrice
from #tmp inner join RTO_Calculator.dbo.Term as t
on #tmp.CenterCity = t.CenterCity and #tmp.CenterCity = t.CityService
and #tmp.PayWeihgt>=t.MinMass and #tmp.PayWeihgt<=t.MaxMass
and #tmp.Type = t.Type and #tmp.SendCity = t.SendCity

update #tmp set WeightTariff=0 where PayWeihgt*WeightTariff<MinTariff
--select * from #tmp where CenterCity='Воронеж'
update dbo.OrderAddress set
TerminalTariff = #tmp.WeightTariff,
MinTerminalTariff =case when #tmp.WeightTariff=0 then   #tmp.MinTariff else 0 end,
CenterCityQty = RowQnt
from dbo.OrderAddress inner join #tmp on dbo.OrderAddress.CenterCity = #tmp.CenterCity
and OrderAddress.SendCity = #tmp.SendCity
and OrderAddress.Type = #tmp.Type
where OrderId=@ID and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
 update dbo.OrderAddress set PayWeightSet = case when Vol*250>Weight then Vol*250 else Weight end where OrderId=@ID and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
 update dbo.OrderAddress set TerminalPrice = case when TerminalTariff > 0 then PayWeightSet*TerminalTariff else MinTerminalTariff/CenterCityQty end where OrderId=@ID and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
--select * from #tmp
drop table #tmp
select CenterCity, CityName, COUNT(1) as rto_qty, CAST(0 as int) as L , CAST(0 as int) as L_qty , CAST(0 as int) as L_Vol , [TYPE],[SendCity]
into #tmp1
from dbo.OrderAddressView where OrderId=@ID and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
--and CenterCity='Хабаровск'
group by CenterCity, CityName , [TYPE],[SendCity]

update #tmp1 set L= (select top 1  L from RTO_Calculator.dbo.Term as t where t.CenterCity = #tmp1.CenterCity and t.CityService = #tmp1.CityName 
and t.[Type]=#tmp1.[Type] and t.[SendCity]=#tmp1.[SendCity] )

--select * from #tmp1

if @Point=0
update #tmp1 set L_qty = case
	when L=0 then CEILING(cast(rto_qty as real) / 3)
	when (L>0) and (L<=50) then CEILING(cast(rto_qty as real) / 5)
	else CEILING(cast(rto_qty as real) / 4) end,
	L_Vol = case
	when L=0 then  3
	when (L>0) and (L<=50) then  5
	else   4 end
else
 
 update #tmp1 set L_qty = rto_qty ,
	L_Vol = 1

declare @CenterCity varchar(100),
@CityName varchar(100),
@Qty int,
@L_Vol int,
@Type nvarchar(50),
@SendCity nvarchar(250)
--select * from #tmp1

declare mc1 cursor for
select  CenterCity , CityName, L_Qty,L_Vol from #tmp1 order by CenterCity, CityName
open mc1
fetch mc1 into @CenterCity, @CityName, @Qty, @L_Vol
declare @i int, @j int
declare @Rowid uniqueidentifier
update OrderAddress set _CityName = OrderAddressView.CityName
from OrderAddress inner join OrderAddressView on OrderAddress.Id=OrderAddressView.Id
where OrderAddress.OrderId=@id
update OrderAddress set RouteNumber=null where OrderId=@ID

SET ROWCOUNT 1
while @@FETCH_STATUS=0 begin
	set @i=1
	
	while @i<=@Qty begin
		set @j=1
		while @j<=@L_Vol begin
			--@L_Vol раз присвоить @i в номер маршрута
			--select top 1 @Rowid = ID from [dbo].[OrderAddressView] where OrderId=@ID 
			--and CityName = @CityName and CenterCity=@CenterCity

			update OrderAddress set RouteNumber=@i where OrderId=@ID 
			and _CityName = @CityName and CenterCity=@CenterCity and RouteNumber is null and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
			set @j=@j+1
			
		end
		set @i=@i+1
	end
	fetch mc1 into @CenterCity, @CityName, @Qty, @L_Vol

close mc1
deallocate mc1

into #tmp2
from
(select _CityName, CenterCity, RouteNumber, sum(Vol) as Vol, SendCity, Type
from [OrderAddress]
where OrderId=@ID  and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
group by _CityName, CenterCity, RouteNumber, SendCity , Type)
 as T inner join RTO_Calculator.dbo.Vol as v on T.CenterCity = v.CenterCity
 and T._CityName = v.CityService and T.SendCity = v.SendCity and T.Type = v.Type
 
 and t.Vol >=v.MinV and T.Vol<v.MaxV

 update OrderAddress set
 TransCityTariff = #tmp2.TransCityPrice
,InternalTariff = #tmp2.InternalPrice

 and OrderAddress.SendCity =#tmp2.SendCity and OrderAddress.Type =#tmp2.Type 
 where OrderId=@ID  and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0


 update OrderAddress set RouteVol = (select SUM(vol) from OrderAddress as t where t.CenterCity = OrderAddress.CenterCity and t._cityName = OrderAddress._CityName and t.RouteNumber =OrderAddress.RouteNumber and OrderId=@ID and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0)
 where OrderId=@ID  and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
 update OrderAddress set TransCityPrice =Vol/RouteVol*TransCityTariff where OrderId=@ID and RouteVol>0
 update OrderAddress set L= (select top 1  L from RTO_Calculator.dbo.Term as t where t.CenterCity = OrderAddress.CenterCity and t.CityService = OrderAddress._CityName and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
 and t.SendCity = OrderAddress.SendCity and t.Type = OrderAddress.Type
 )
 where OrderId=@ID  and ISNULL(Closed,0)=0
 drop table #tmp2

 and t.SendCity = OrderAddress.SendCity)

mdlz.dbo.CalcDistr 
CREATE  procedure CalcDistr(@ID uniqueidentifier) as
begin
if exists(select 1 from DistrRequest where Id=@ID and SelfDelivery=1)
	begin
		update DistrRequest set 
			Price = 0, CityRcId=null
		where DistrRequest.Id = @ID
		return
	end
 update DistrRequestTab set Weight = DistrRequestTab.Qty * Product.Weight, Vol = DistrRequestTab.Qty * Product.Vol 
 from DistrRequestTab inner join Product on DistrRequestTab.ProductId = Product.Id
 where  DocID = @ID
 update DistrRequest set Weight = (select SUM(weight) from DistrRequestTab where DistrRequestTab.DocID = DistrRequest.Id),
	Vol = (select SUM(Vol) from DistrRequestTab where DistrRequestTab.DocID = DistrRequest.Id)
	where Id = @ID
update DistrRequest
set PayWeight = case when Vol*250>Weight then Vol*250 else Weight end where Id=@ID

declare @MinTariff decimal(18,2), @transtariff decimal(18,2)
declare @CityService nvarchar(100), @CenterCity nvarchar(100)
select @CityService = City.CityName from City inner join DistrRequest on DistrRequest.ToCityId = City.Id where DistrRequest.Id=@ID
select top 1 @CenterCity = CenterCity from RTO_Calculator.dbo.Term  where CityService=@CityService
print @CityService 
print @CenterCity 
select @MinTariff = t.MinPrice
from RTO_Calculator.dbo.Term as t
where t.CenterCity = t.CityService and t.CenterCity = @CenterCity and SendCity = 'Домодедово'
select @transtariff = t.Tariff
from RTO_Calculator.dbo.Term as t
cross join DistrRequest
where t.CenterCity = t.CityService and t.CenterCity = @CenterCity and SendCity = 'Домодедово'
and DistrRequest.PayWeight>=t.MinMass and DistrRequest.PayWeight<=t.MaxMass
and DistrRequest.Id = @ID
print @MinTariff 
print @transtariff 
update DistrRequest set TerminalTariff = case when @transtariff*PayWeight> @MinTariff then @transtariff*PayWeight else @MinTariff end where Id=@ID
update DistrRequest set TransCityPrice = V.TransCityPrice,InternalPrice = v.InternalPrice  from
DistrRequest inner join RTO_Calculator.dbo.Vol as v
on  @CenterCity = v.CenterCity
 and @CityService = v.CityService and  v.SendCity= 'Домодедово' and  v.Type ='LTL'
 and DistrRequest.Vol >=v.MinV and DistrRequest.Vol<v.MaxV
where DistrRequest.Id = @ID

update DistrRequest set 
Price = TerminalTariff + TransCityPrice +InternalPrice,
CityRcId = (select Id from City where CityName = @CenterCity)
where DistrRequest.Id = @ID

end
mdlz.dbo.CalcVol 
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[CalcVol](@OrderID uniqueidentifier)
AS
BEGIN
update OrderAddress set Vol =(SELECT     SUM( 
    Case when Product.VolUnit>=0.01 then  Product.VolUnit* OrderAddressEquipment.Count 
else  CEILING(Width * Height * Length / case when CountInPack= 0 then 1 else CountInPack end / 10000000)/100 * OrderAddressEquipment.Count 
end
)
FROM                OrderEquipment INNER JOIN
                  Product ON OrderEquipment.ProductId = Product.Id INNER JOIN
                  OrderAddressEquipment ON OrderEquipment.Id = OrderAddressEquipment.EquipmentId
where OrderAddressEquipment.AddressId = OrderAddress.ID),
Weight = (SELECT     SUM( Product.UnitWeight* OrderAddressEquipment.Count)
FROM                OrderEquipment INNER JOIN
                  Product ON OrderEquipment.ProductId = Product.Id INNER JOIN
                  OrderAddressEquipment ON OrderEquipment.Id = OrderAddressEquipment.EquipmentId
where OrderAddressEquipment.AddressId = OrderAddress.ID)
where OrderAddress.OrderId=@OrderID
END

mdlz.dbo.DistrRequestPost 
CREATE procedure [dbo].[DistrRequestPost](@DocID uniqueidentifier, @Posted bit, @Error nvarchar null OUT) as
begin 
	 if @Posted=1 begin
		create table #tmpReport (Id uniqueidentifier, SapCode nvarchar(50), Name nvarchar(200), qtyinPack int, PackPerPallet int, IncomeDate smalldatetime null, 
		Qty int,
		Pallet decimal(18,2),
		Blocked int,
		Reserved int,
		ReservedByRequest int,
		ReservedByDistr int null,
		FreeQty int)

	
		insert into #tmpReport exec ReportProduct
		select ProductId, sum(qty) as qty 
		into #tmp
		from DistrRequestTab
		where DocID = @DocID 
		group by ProductId
		update #tmpReport set FreeQty = FreeQty - #tmp.qty
		from #tmpReport inner join #tmp on  #tmpReport.Id = #tmp.ProductId
		if exists( select 1 from  #tmpReport where FreeQty<0 and Id in (select ProductID from #tmp)) begin
			print 'ошибка';
			return;
		end;
		drop table #tmpReport
		update DistrRequest
		set IsSended =1, SendDate = GETDATE()
		where Id=@DocID
	end
	else 
		update DistrRequest
		set IsSended =0, SendDate = null
		where Id=@DocID
end

end
close cr
deallocate cr

mdlz.dbo.ReportInitiative 

CREATE procedure [dbo].[ReportInitiative] (@beginDate smalldatetime='1-oct-2023', @endDate smalldatetime ='31-dec-2023') as
begin
declare @d int, @m int, @y int;
 select @beginDate =DATEFROMPARTS (datepart(yyyy,@beginDate), datepart(mm,@beginDate), 1 )
SELECT [oa].[NetworkName], [oa].[PlacementPeriod], [p].[Name], SUBSTRING(SapCode,4,7) as SapCode,  [o].Number AS APNumber, SUM( [oae].Count) as [Count], o.WorkName
FROM  [OrderEquipment] AS [oe]
inner join [Order] AS [o] on [o].[Id] = [oe].[OrderId]
inner join [Product] AS [p] on [p].[Id] = [oe].[ProductId]
inner join [OrderAddressEquipment] AS [oae] on [oae].[EquipmentId] = [oe].[Id]
inner join [OrderAddress] As [oa] on [oa].[Id] = [oae].AddressId
where [o].Month between @beginDate and  @endDate 
group by [oa].[NetworkName], [oa].[PlacementPeriod], [p].[Name], [p].[SapCode], [o].Number, o.WorkName
end

BEGIN

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ReportTask] 
	(@BeginDate smalldatetime=null, @EndDate smalldatetime = null)
AS
BEGIN
SELECT        [Order].Number as OrderNumber, OrderAddress.InternalNumber, OrderAddress.SFIS, OrderAddress.City, OrderAddress.Address, OrderAddress.OrderId, OrderAddress.Id, [Order].ConfirmedAt, [Order].WorkName, 
                         OrderServiceType.Name AS ServiceType, t.EventName, t.Deviation, OrderAddress.NetworkName, OrderAddress.WarehouseFromCity, OrderAddress.CenterCity, OrderAddress.Number, OrderAddress.Vol, 
                         OrderAddress.MerchName, OrderAddress.KAE, OrderAddress.EmployeeName, OrderAddress.EmployeePhone, OrderAddress.DeliveryBy, OrderAddress.Weight, OrderAddress.DistanceToCenter, OrderAddress.FEM, 
                         OrderAddress.ManagerName, OrderAddress.ManagerPhone, OrderAddress.Closed, OrderAddress.Confirmed, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty1, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty2, 
                         GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty3, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty4, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty5, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty6, 
                         GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.SapCode1, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.SapCode2, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.SapCode3, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.SapCode4, 
                         GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.SapCode5, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.SapCode6, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty1, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty2, 
                         GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty3, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty4, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty5, GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty6,
ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty1,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty2,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty3,0)+
ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty4,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty5,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty6,0) 
as PlanQty,
ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty1,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty2,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty3,0)+
ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty4,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty5,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty6,0)
as FactQty,
ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty1,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty2,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty3,0)+
ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty4,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty5,0)+ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.PlanQty6,0) 
-
ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty1,0)-ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty2,0)-ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty3,0)-
ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty4,0)-ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty5,0)-ISNULL(GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.FactQty6,0)
 as Delta,
 GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.MountID
FROM            OrderAddress INNER JOIN
                         [Order] ON OrderAddress.OrderId = [Order].Id INNER JOIN
                         OrderServiceType ON [Order].ServiceTypeId = OrderServiceType.Id LEFT OUTER JOIN

                         GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC ON OrderAddress.InternalNumber = GlobalBase.dbo.RTO_WebReportsViewLC.InternalNumber 
						 where [Order].CreatedAt between @BeginDate and @EndDate
END
mdlz.dbo.ReportVol 
CREATE procedure [dbo].[ReportVol]( @BeginDate smalldatetime='20-mar-2023',
		@EndDate smallDateTime= '31-mar-2023', @Sum bit=0) as

 select t.SapCode, SUM(Qty) as Qty, Product.Name ,
 Product.CountInPack, Product.[PacksPerPallet]
 into #tmp1
 from
(select SapCode, SUM(Qty) as Qty from WHMoveView
where WHIndex = 'RU88' and date <@BeginDate and ID not In (403,405)
group by SapCode
having SUM(Qty)>0
union
select SapCode, 0 from WHMoveView
where WHIndex = 'RU88' and date between @BeginDate and @EndDate+1  and ID not In (403,405)) as t
inner join Product on Product.SapCode=t.SapCode
group by t.SapCode, Product.Name,
 Product.CountInPack, Product.[PacksPerPallet]
--select * from #tmp1 order by SapCode
 select SapCode, CountInPack, [PacksPerPallet],
 Qty as BeginDayQty,
  isnull((select SUM(Qty) from WHMoveView where Date >=@BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and Qty>0 and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp1.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405)),0) as IncomeQty,
  isnull((select SUM(-Qty) from WHMoveView where Date >=@BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and Qty<0 and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp1.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405)),0) as OutcomeQty,
  Qty + isnull((select SUM(Qty) from WHMoveView where Date >=@BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp1.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405)),0) as EndDayQty,
 
  @BeginDate as Date,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as BeginDayPallet,
 cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as IncomePallet,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as OutcomePallet,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as EndDayPallet,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as PayPallet,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as BeginDayVol,
   cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as IncomeVol,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as OutcomeVol,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as EndDayVol
  into #tmp2
 from #tmp1



 set @BeginDate=@BeginDate+1
 while @BeginDate<=@EndDate begin
	print @BeginDate
	insert into #tmp2(SapCode, CountInPack, [PacksPerPallet], Date, BeginDayQty, EndDayQty,IncomeQty, OutcomeQty)
	(
	  select SapCode , CountInPack, [PacksPerPallet], @BeginDate,EndDayQty, --конец предыдущего дня
	  EndDayQty+isnull((select SUM(Qty) from WHMoveView where  Date >= @BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405)),0),
	  isnull((select SUM(Qty) from WHMoveView where  Date >= @BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and Qty>0 and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405)),0) ,
		isnull((select SUM(-Qty) from WHMoveView where  Date >= @BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and Qty<0 and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405)),0) 
  
	  from #tmp2 where Date = @BeginDate-1
	)
	set @BeginDate=@BeginDate+1
 end;
 update  #tmp2 set IncomePallet = ceiling(cast(IncomeQty as real) / CountInPack) /[PacksPerPallet],
 OutcomePallet =  ceiling(cast(OutcomeQty as real) / CountInPack) /[PacksPerPallet], 
 EndDayPallet =  ceiling(cast(EndDayQty as real) / CountInPack) /[PacksPerPallet],
 BeginDayPallet = ceiling(cast(BeginDayQty as real) / CountInPack) /[PacksPerPallet]
 
  
  update  #tmp2 set PayPallet = (BeginDayPallet+IncomePallet),
  IncomeVol = IncomeQty* (select Product.VolUnit from Product where Product.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode),
   OutcomeVol = OutcomeQty* (select Product.VolUnit from Product where Product.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode),
    EndDayVol = EndDayQty* (select Product.VolUnit from Product where Product.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode),
 BeginDayVol = cast(BeginDayQty as real) * (select Product.VolUnit from Product where Product.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode)

ALTER TABLE #tmp2 ADD QtyPallet decimal(18,1) null, BoxPiсking int null, QtyPicking int null ;

update #tmp2 set  BoxPiсking =OutcomeQty / CountInPack, QtyPicking = OutcomeQty % CountInPack		

 if @Sum=0
	select SUBSTRING(#tmp2.SapCode,4,7) as SapCode, #tmp2.CountInPack, #tmp2.PacksPerPallet, #tmp2.BeginDayQty, #tmp2.IncomeQty, #tmp2.OutcomeQty, #tmp2.EndDayQty, 
	#tmp2.Date, #tmp2.BeginDayPallet, #tmp2.IncomePallet, #tmp2.OutcomePallet, #tmp2.EndDayPallet, #tmp2.PayPallet, #tmp2.BeginDayVol, 
	#tmp2.IncomeVol, #tmp2.OutcomeVol, #tmp2.EndDayVol , #tmp1.Name, #tmp2.BoxPiсking, #tmp2.QtyPicking 
	
	from #tmp1 inner join #tmp2 on #tmp1.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode
	order by #tmp2.Date,#tmp2.SapCode
 else
	select date, SUM(BeginDayPallet) as BeginDayPallet, 
	SUM(IncomePallet) as IncomePallet, 
	SUM(OutcomePallet) as OutcomePallet, 
	SUM(EndDayPallet) as EndDayPallet, 
	SUM(PayPallet) as PayPallet, 
	SUM(BeginDayVol) as BeginDayVol, 
	SUM(IncomeVol) as IncomeVol, 
	SUM(OutcomeVol) as OutcomeVol, 
	SUM(EndDayVol) as EndDayVol
	
	from #tmp2 group by date order by date
	
 drop table #tmp1
 drop table #tmp2
mdlz.dbo.ReportVolToday 
CREATE procedure [dbo].[ReportVolToday]
as
declare
@BeginDate smalldatetime, 
@EndDate smallDateTime, 
@Sum bit

set @Sum=0;
set @BeginDate = cast(GETDATE() as date)
set @EndDate = cast(GETDATE() as date)
--CAST( WareHouseDoc.Date as date) as Date

 select t.SapCode, SUM(Qty) as Qty, Product.Name ,
 Product.CountInPack, Product.[PacksPerPallet]
 into #tmp1
 from
(select SapCode, SUM(Qty) as Qty from WHMoveView
where WHIndex = 'RU88' and date <@BeginDate  and ID not In (403,405) 
group by SapCode
having SUM(Qty)>0
union
select SapCode, 0 from WHMoveView
where WHIndex = 'RU88' and date between @BeginDate and @EndDate+1  and ID not In (403,405) ) as t
inner join Product on Product.SapCode=t.SapCode
group by t.SapCode, Product.Name,
 Product.CountInPack, Product.[PacksPerPallet]
--select * from #tmp1 order by SapCode
 select SapCode, CountInPack, [PacksPerPallet],
 Qty as BeginDayQty,
  isnull((select SUM(Qty) from WHMoveView where Date >=@BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and Qty>0 and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp1.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405) ),0) as IncomeQty,
  isnull((select SUM(-Qty) from WHMoveView where Date >=@BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and Qty<0 and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp1.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405) ),0) as OutcomeQty,
  Qty + isnull((select SUM(Qty) from WHMoveView where Date >=@BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp1.SapCode  and ID not In (403,405) ),0) as EndDayQty,
 
  @BeginDate as Date,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as BeginDayPallet,
 cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as IncomePallet,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as OutcomePallet,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as EndDayPallet,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as PayPallet,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as BeginDayVol,
   cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as IncomeVol,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as OutcomeVol,
  cast(0 as decimal(18,2)) as EndDayVol
  into #tmp2
 from #tmp1



 set @BeginDate=@BeginDate+1
 while @BeginDate<=@EndDate begin
	print @BeginDate
	insert into #tmp2(SapCode, CountInPack, [PacksPerPallet], Date, BeginDayQty, EndDayQty,IncomeQty, OutcomeQty)
	(
	  select SapCode , CountInPack, [PacksPerPallet], @BeginDate,EndDayQty, --конец предыдущего дня
	  EndDayQty+isnull((select SUM(Qty) from WHMoveView where  Date >= @BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode and ID not In (403,405) ),0),
	  isnull((select SUM(Qty) from WHMoveView where  Date >= @BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and Qty>0 and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode and ID not In (403,405)),0) ,
	  isnull((select SUM(-Qty) from WHMoveView where  Date >= @BeginDate and Date<@BeginDate+1 and WHIndex = 'RU88' and Qty<0 and WHMoveView.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode and ID not In (403,405)),0) 
  
	  from #tmp2 where Date = @BeginDate-1
	)
	set @BeginDate=@BeginDate+1
 end;
 update  #tmp2 set IncomePallet = ceiling(cast(IncomeQty as real) / CountInPack) /[PacksPerPallet],
 OutcomePallet =  ceiling(cast(OutcomeQty as real) / CountInPack) /[PacksPerPallet], 
 EndDayPallet =  ceiling(cast(EndDayQty as real) / CountInPack) /[PacksPerPallet],
 BeginDayPallet = ceiling(cast(BeginDayQty as real) / CountInPack) /[PacksPerPallet]
 
  
  update  #tmp2 set PayPallet = (BeginDayPallet+IncomePallet),
  IncomeVol = IncomeQty* (select Product.VolUnit from Product where Product.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode),
   OutcomeVol = OutcomeQty* (select Product.VolUnit from Product where Product.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode),
    EndDayVol = EndDayQty* (select Product.VolUnit from Product where Product.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode),
 BeginDayVol = cast(BeginDayQty as real) * (select Product.VolUnit from Product where Product.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode)
 if @Sum=0
	select SUBSTRING(#tmp2.SapCode,4,7) as SapCode, #tmp2.CountInPack, #tmp2.PacksPerPallet, #tmp2.BeginDayQty, #tmp2.IncomeQty, #tmp2.OutcomeQty, #tmp2.EndDayQty, 
	#tmp2.Date, #tmp2.BeginDayPallet, #tmp2.IncomePallet, #tmp2.OutcomePallet, #tmp2.EndDayPallet, #tmp2.PayPallet, #tmp2.BeginDayVol, 
	#tmp2.IncomeVol, #tmp2.OutcomeVol, #tmp2.EndDayVol , #tmp1.Name from #tmp1 inner join #tmp2 on #tmp1.SapCode = #tmp2.SapCode
	order by #tmp2.Date,#tmp2.SapCode
 else
	select date, SUM(BeginDayPallet) as BeginDayPallet, 
	SUM(IncomePallet) as IncomePallet, 
	SUM(OutcomePallet) as OutcomePallet, 
	SUM(EndDayPallet) as EndDayPallet, 
	SUM(PayPallet) as PayPallet, 
	SUM(BeginDayVol) as BeginDayVol, 
	SUM(IncomeVol) as IncomeVol, 
	SUM(OutcomeVol) as OutcomeVol, 
	SUM(EndDayVol) as EndDayVol
	
	from #tmp2 group by date order by date
	
 drop table #tmp1
 drop table #tmp2

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[SFMgr]
   (@OldID 	[uniqueidentifier]=null,
   @NewID	  [uniqueidentifier] =null output,
   @Action	[int],
   @Number    [varchar](255)=null,
   @AccountNumber    [varchar](255)=null,
   @DateTime    [datetime]=null,
   @Currency    [varchar](50)=null,
   @Summa    [decimal](18, 4)=null,
   @InvoiceID    [uniqueidentifier]=null,
   @SumRub    [decimal](18, 2)=null,
   @AppendixID    [uniqueidentifier]=null,
   @DogovorID	uniqueidentifier=null,
   @ContragentID uniqueidentifier=null,
   @ContractorID	uniqueidentifier=null)
AS
declare
	@InternalNumber int
declare @InsertUserID uniqueidentifier
SELECT @InsertUserID=PersonID from personal where UserName= user_name(user_ID())
	
if @Action=0
 delete from [dbo].[SF]  where [ID]=@OldID
else
 if @OldID='{00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000}'
   begin
     set @NewID=NewID()
     select @InternalNumber=MAX(InternalNumber) +1 from SF 
     INSERT INTO[dbo].[SF]
       ( [ID],
      [Number],
      [AccountNumber],
      [DateTime],
      [Currency],
      [Summa],
      [InvoiceID],
      [SumRub],
      [AppendixID],
      [InternalNumber],
      [Visible],
      DogovorID,
	  ContragentID,
      ContractorID, 
      InsertDate,
	  InsertUserID)
   VALUES
     (@NewID,
      @Number,
      @AccountNumber,
      @DateTime,
      @Currency,
      @Summa,
      @InvoiceID,
      @SumRub,
      @AppendixID,
      @InternalNumber,
      1,
      @DogovorID,
	  @ContragentID,
      @ContractorID,
      dbo.RoundDate2008(GetDate()), 
      @InsertUserID)
     END
   ELSE
     BEGIN
       set @NewID=@OldID
       UPDATE [dbo].[SF] set
       [Number]= @Number,
       [AccountNumber]= @AccountNumber,
       [DateTime]= @DateTime,
       [Currency]= @Currency,
       [Summa]= @Summa,
       [InvoiceID]= @InvoiceID,
       [SumRub]= @SumRub,
       [AppendixID]= @AppendixID,
       DogovorID = @DogovorID,
	   ContragentID = @ContragentID,
       ContractorID = @ContractorID,
       ModifyDate=dbo.RoundDate2008(getdate()),
       ModifyUserID=@InsertUserID
       WHERE [ID]=@OldID
     END

mdlz.dbo.send_notification 
CREATE procedure [dbo].[send_notification]
AS 
BEGIN
	-- SET NOCOUNT ON added to prevent extra result sets from
	-- interfering with SELECT statements.
	SET NOCOUNT ON;
    declare @OrderID uniqueidentifier,
	@ID uniqueidentifier,
	@StatusID int
	
	select top 1 @OrderID=OrderID, @StatusID=[Status], @ID=OrderStatuses.ID from OrderStatuses inner join [Order] on OrderStatuses.OrderId=[Order].Id
	
	where ISNULL(mail_sended,0)=0 and [Order].ServiceTypeId not in ( '985B88B3-F415-4FC1-AC81-082F428FB524', 'CCAEAD11-9B10-4C66-9DC4-695B0B30FBA1','1C05A750-3522-48F6-9050-A1DAD6E254C3')
	order by OrderStatuses.CreatedAt
	
	if @StatusID in (0,1,2,3,4) begin
		declare @mBody varchar(1000),
		@APNumber int,
		@APName varchar(500),
		@mSubj varchar(500)
		
		select @APNumber = Number, @APName = WorkName from[Order] where Id = @OrderID
		if @StatusID =0 begin
			set @mSubj = 'Создана новая АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
			set @mBody = 'Создана новая АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
		end
		if @StatusID =1 begin
			set @mSubj = 'Загружена АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
			set @mBody = 'Загружена АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
		end
		if @StatusID =2 begin
			set @mSubj = 'Смета готова АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
			set @mBody = 'Смета готова АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
		end
		if @StatusID =3 begin
			set @mSubj = 'Подтверждена АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
			set @mBody = 'Подтверждена АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
		end
		if @StatusID =4 begin
			set @mSubj = 'Принята в работу АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
			set @mBody = 'Принята в работу АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
		end
		declare @mrecipients varchar(500)
		select @mrecipients = coalesce(@mrecipients + ';', '') +  convert(varchar(100),address)
		from OrderStatusesMail
		where StatusID=@StatusID

		EXEC msdb.dbo.sp_send_dbmail @profile_name = 'External', @recipients = @mrecipients
		,@body =@mBody ,  @subject =  @mSubj;
		
	
	end
	update OrderStatuses set mail_sended=1 where Id=@ID
	
	--if exists(select 1 from FileEstiAdjust where ISNULL(mail_sended,0)=0 and Stereotype='estimate') begin
	--	select @OrderID=OrderID,  @ID=ID from FileEstiAdjust where ISNULL(mail_sended,0)=0 and Stereotype='estimate'
	--	select @APNumber = Number, @APName = WorkName from[Order] where Id = @OrderID
	--	select @mrecipients = coalesce(@mrecipients + ';', '') +  convert(varchar(100),address)
	--	from OrderStatusesMail
	--	where StatusID=101
	--	set @mSubj = 'Драфт сметы создан';
	--	set @mBody = 'Драфт сметы создан АП №'+CAST(@APNumber as varchar(10))+' '+@APName
			
	--	EXEC msdb.dbo.sp_send_dbmail @profile_name = 'External', @recipients = @mrecipients
	--	,@body =@mBody ,  @subject =  @mSubj;
	--	update FileEstiAdjust set mail_sended=1 where Id=@ID
	--end
end
mdlz.dbo.sp_alterdiagram 
	CREATE PROCEDURE dbo.sp_alterdiagram
	(
		@diagramname 	sysname,
		@owner_id	int	= null,
		@version 	int,
		@definition 	varbinary(max)
	)
	WITH EXECUTE AS 'dbo'
	AS
	BEGIN
		set nocount on
	
		declare @theId 			int
		declare @retval 		int
		declare @IsDbo 			int
		
		declare @UIDFound 		int
		declare @DiagId			int
		declare @ShouldChangeUID	int
	
		if(@diagramname is null)
		begin
			RAISERROR ('Invalid ARG', 16, 1)
			return -1
		end
	
		execute as caller;
		select @theId = DATABASE_PRINCIPAL_ID();	 
		select @IsDbo = IS_MEMBER(N'db_owner'); 
		if(@owner_id is null)
			select @owner_id = @theId;
		revert;
	
		select @ShouldChangeUID = 0
		select @DiagId = diagram_id, @UIDFound = principal_id from dbo.sysdiagrams where principal_id = @owner_id and name = @diagramname 
		
		if(@DiagId IS NULL or (@IsDbo = 0 and @theId <> @UIDFound))
		begin
			RAISERROR ('Diagram does not exist or you do not have permission.', 16, 1);
			return -3
		end
	
		if(@IsDbo <> 0)
		begin
			if(@UIDFound is null or USER_NAME(@UIDFound) is null) -- invalid principal_id
			begin
				select @ShouldChangeUID = 1 ;
			end
		end
		-- update dds data			
		update dbo.sysdiagrams set definition = @definition where diagram_id = @DiagId ;
		-- change owner
		if(@ShouldChangeUID = 1)
			update dbo.sysdiagrams set principal_id = @theId where diagram_id = @DiagId ;
		-- update dds version
		if(@version is not null)
			update dbo.sysdiagrams set version = @version where diagram_id = @DiagId ;
		return 0
	END
mdlz.dbo.sp_creatediagram 
	CREATE PROCEDURE dbo.sp_creatediagram
	(
		@diagramname 	sysname,
		@owner_id		int	= null, 	
		@version 		int,
		@definition 	varbinary(max)
	)
	WITH EXECUTE AS 'dbo'
	AS
	BEGIN
		set nocount on
	
		declare @theId int
		declare @retval int
		declare @IsDbo	int
		declare @userName sysname
		if(@version is null or @diagramname is null)
		begin
			RAISERROR (N'E_INVALIDARG', 16, 1);
			return -1
		end
	
		execute as caller;
		select @theId = DATABASE_PRINCIPAL_ID(); 
		select @IsDbo = IS_MEMBER(N'db_owner');
		revert; 
		
		if @owner_id is null
		begin
			select @owner_id = @theId;
		end
		else
		begin
			if @theId <> @owner_id
			begin
				if @IsDbo = 0
				begin
					RAISERROR (N'E_INVALIDARG', 16, 1);
					return -1
				end
				select @theId = @owner_id
			end
		end
		-- next 2 line only for test, will be removed after define name unique
		if EXISTS(select diagram_id from dbo.sysdiagrams where principal_id = @theId and name = @diagramname)
		begin
			RAISERROR ('The name is already used.', 16, 1);
			return -2
		end
	
		insert into dbo.sysdiagrams(name, principal_id , version, definition)
				VALUES(@diagramname, @theId, @version, @definition) ;
		
		select @retval = @@IDENTITY 
		return @retval
	END

mdlz.dbo.sp_helpdiagrams 
	CREATE PROCEDURE dbo.sp_helpdiagrams
	(
		@diagramname sysname = NULL,
		@owner_id int = NULL
	)
	WITH EXECUTE AS N'dbo'
	AS
	BEGIN
		DECLARE @user sysname
		DECLARE @dboLogin bit
		EXECUTE AS CALLER;
			SET @user = USER_NAME();
			SET @dboLogin = CONVERT(bit,IS_MEMBER('db_owner'));
		REVERT;
		SELECT
			[Database] = DB_NAME(),
			[Name] = name,
			[ID] = diagram_id,
			[Owner] = USER_NAME(principal_id),
			[OwnerID] = principal_id
		FROM
			sysdiagrams
		WHERE
			(@dboLogin = 1 OR USER_NAME(principal_id) = @user) AND
			(@diagramname IS NULL OR name = @diagramname) AND
			(@owner_id IS NULL OR principal_id = @owner_id)
		ORDER BY
			4, 5, 1
	END
mdlz.dbo.sp_renamediagram 
	CREATE PROCEDURE dbo.sp_renamediagram
	(
		@diagramname 		sysname,
		@owner_id		int	= null,
		@new_diagramname	sysname
	
	)
	WITH EXECUTE AS 'dbo'
	AS
	BEGIN
		set nocount on
		declare @theId 			int
		declare @IsDbo 			int
		
		declare @UIDFound 		int
		declare @DiagId			int
		declare @DiagIdTarg		int
		declare @u_name			sysname
		if((@diagramname is null) or (@new_diagramname is null))
		begin
			RAISERROR ('Invalid value', 16, 1);
			return -1
		end
	
		EXECUTE AS CALLER;
		select @theId = DATABASE_PRINCIPAL_ID();
		select @IsDbo = IS_MEMBER(N'db_owner'); 
		if(@owner_id is null)
			select @owner_id = @theId;
		REVERT;
	
		select @u_name = USER_NAME(@owner_id)
	
		select @DiagId = diagram_id, @UIDFound = principal_id from dbo.sysdiagrams where principal_id = @owner_id and name = @diagramname 
		if(@DiagId IS NULL or (@IsDbo = 0 and @UIDFound <> @theId))
		begin
			RAISERROR ('Diagram does not exist or you do not have permission.', 16, 1)
			return -3
		end
	
		-- if((@u_name is not null) and (@new_diagramname = @diagramname))	-- nothing will change
		--	return 0;
	
		if(@u_name is null)
			select @DiagIdTarg = diagram_id from dbo.sysdiagrams where principal_id = @theId and name = @new_diagramname
		else
			select @DiagIdTarg = diagram_id from dbo.sysdiagrams where principal_id = @owner_id and name = @new_diagramname
	
		if((@DiagIdTarg is not null) and  @DiagId <> @DiagIdTarg)
		begin
			RAISERROR ('The name is already used.', 16, 1);
			return -2
		end		
	
		if(@u_name is null)
			update dbo.sysdiagrams set [name] = @new_diagramname, principal_id = @theId where diagram_id = @DiagId
		else
			update dbo.sysdiagrams set [name] = @new_diagramname where diagram_id = @DiagId
		return 0
	END
mdlz.dbo.sp_upgraddiagrams 
	CREATE PROCEDURE dbo.sp_upgraddiagrams
	AS
	BEGIN
		IF OBJECT_ID(N'dbo.sysdiagrams') IS NOT NULL
			return 0;
	
		CREATE TABLE dbo.sysdiagrams
		(
			name sysname NOT NULL,
			principal_id int NOT NULL,	-- we may change it to varbinary(85)
			diagram_id int PRIMARY KEY IDENTITY,
			version int,
	
			definition varbinary(max)
			CONSTRAINT UK_principal_name UNIQUE
			(
				principal_id,
				name
			)
		);

		/* Add this if we need to have some form of extended properties for diagrams */
		/*
		IF OBJECT_ID(N'dbo.sysdiagram_properties') IS NULL
		BEGIN
			CREATE TABLE dbo.sysdiagram_properties
			(
				diagram_id int,
				name sysname,
				value varbinary(max) NOT NULL
			)
		END
		*/
		IF OBJECT_ID(N'dbo.dtproperties') IS NOT NULL
		begin
			insert into dbo.sysdiagrams
			(
				[name],
				[principal_id],
				[version],
				[definition]
			)
			select	 
				convert(sysname, dgnm.[uvalue]),
				DATABASE_PRINCIPAL_ID(N'dbo'),			-- will change to the sid of sa
				0,							-- zero for old format, dgdef.[version],
				dgdef.[lvalue]
			from dbo.[dtproperties] dgnm
				inner join dbo.[dtproperties] dggd on dggd.[property] = 'DtgSchemaGUID' and dggd.[objectid] = dgnm.[objectid]	
				inner join dbo.[dtproperties] dgdef on dgdef.[property] = 'DtgSchemaDATA' and dgdef.[objectid] = dgnm.[objectid]
				
			where dgnm.[property] = 'DtgSchemaNAME' and dggd.[uvalue] like N'_EA3E6268-D998-11CE-9454-00AA00A3F36E_' 
			return 2;
		end
		return 1;
	END
